{"tid":2516059,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【淘寶笑料】淘發光手環睇Mirror演唱會撐偶像　鏡粉口語英文夾雜令賣家誤會：是我做錯","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:36:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c44a2710ddfa3ef46f52818870f780116ec77db6","tid":2516059,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"Mirror演唱會即將在5月6日起舉行，姜濤、Ian、Anson Lo、Jer等Mirror成員連日苦練，希望以最佳狀態演出！而一眾鏡粉（Mirror粉絲稱號）也密密支持偶像，有人特意淘寶發光手環出席演唱會，可是到貨後發現貨不對版，令他哭笑不得，其他鏡粉見狀也忍不住爆笑。<br />\n<br />\n該名鏡粉淘寶上訂購發光手環，與賣家對話期間，說了「Sorry 咁寫 Mirror Keung Man」，他沒想到賣家未必明港式口語「咁」及英語「Sorry」的意思，結果賣家會錯意，把整句句子印在手環上。<br />\n<br />\n距離演唱會只有幾日，真言「期待咗幾日」的事主見到貨品送到，拆箱前十分興奮，到拆箱後發現貨不對版哭笑不得，最短的時間經歷2種強烈對比的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n他才意識到淘寶賣家不明白口語及英文夾雜的句子，自嘲是自己表達方式令賣家誤會，<br />\n&quot;是我做錯，是我做錯，還求甚麼...等我仲期待咗幾日！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n他把手環及事件分享到「HK mirror fans」，成為一眾鏡粉的笑彈，鏡粉們紛紛表示很好笑，誇張到「笑到噴飯」，又揶揄事主「親，下次要睇稿或再對多次，佢地真係好醒目架！」。<br />\n<br />\n有熱心的鏡粉希望可以幫事主解決困難，問及句子是否印上手環，如果刮掉「咁寫sorry」是否可行。又有人覺得這個手環錯有錯著，覺得是有故事的手環，想要一隻留念，「想排一隻，好funny。」<br />\n<br />\n除了事主訂造手環支持偶像，亦有其他鏡粉訂造手環，他表示怕賣家「太醒」看錯字，需要講3次要寫對，再才放心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/taobao_thumb_20210504_K_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2Ftaobao_thumb_20210504_K_1024.jpg&h=0c1e596b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/178096911_10159843513645409_61094738582932043_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2F178096911_10159843513645409_61094738582932043_n_1024.jpg&h=b062d289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/178096911_10159843513645409_61094738582932043_n1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2F178096911_10159843513645409_61094738582932043_n1_1024.jpg&h=25972fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/3_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2F3_1024.png&h=b169b79b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/10_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2F10_1024.png&h=6d38e097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2948648/2_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2948648%2F2_1024.png&h=6cff6e1e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}